乳饮品的推广事业，随后于2003年进入上海市场。2005年4月，养乐多（中国）投资有限公司在上海成立。如今，养乐多（中国）集团已拥有广州（2处）、天津、无锡（2处）、佛山6处生产基地和53家分公司，并在广东、上海、北京、天津、厦门、福州、衡阳、南昌、昆明开展了家庭配送服务。 数据显示，在养乐多的巅峰时期，其在华日销量高达760.9万瓶，是该细分赛道名副其实的销量“王者”。2023年，养乐多在中国的年销售额达到了65亿元，占据了23%的市场份额。但随着人们对健康的关注，及这个赛道的内卷，养乐多的销售数据出现了一定的波动，截至2023年9月，养乐多在中国市场的日销售量为253万瓶，同比降幅为23%。与巅峰时期760.9万瓶的日销量相比，降幅近70%，这可能是其关闭上海工厂的原因之一。 （参考来源：突发丨养乐多上海公司将解散，工厂已停产）"},"attached_info":"CkAI2++6/uaa481mEAMaCTExMjI3MTk1MyDS29+6BjAAODJAC3IKNjQ3NzA3ODQxOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"74 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c40dc6b7872e5259f85f1d2be8b32b98_l.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1734334206.35777","card_id":"Q_503721239","target":{"id":503721239,"title":"GORE-TEX 滑雪服是必需品吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/503721239","type":"question","created":1638627424,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":36,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[825,3326,122122,685640,3774232],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"10000mg的防水系数是否够用 坐标欧洲，想去阿尔卑斯滑"},"attached_info":"Cj4I2++6/uaa481mEAMaCDc0MjE5MTMyIODwrY0GMAA4JEAMcgk1MDM3MjEyMzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"66 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f0a393d84f1f342293a405cbc540e93_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1734334206.36059","card_id":"Q_413052348","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":413052348,"title":"男生身高不够怎么办，有什么办法长高吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/413052348","type":"question","created":1596958459,"answer_count":703,"follower_count":2046,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"